data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS- BRING ALL OFFERS! You do not want to miss out on this stunning turn key updated property! 2023 updates include Roof, kitchen, bathrooms, HVAC, hot water heater, flooring and much more! This home boasts a cozy and inviting atmosphere with its charming fireplace, inviting open floor plan to the living room and kitchen. With its great spacious layout, you'll find plenty of space for all your living needs. This home is ready for you to personalize and make it your own. Schedule your showing today! Open House Saturday, January 27th from 2-4PM!
